    <example id="example" otherprops="examples">
      <title>Example</title>
      <p>The following code sample shows how the
          <xmlelement>topicmeta</xmlelement> element can contain a link
        title and short description:</p>
      <codeblock>&lt;map>
  &lt;title>Indexing elements&lt;/title>        
  &lt;topicref href="indexing.dita">
    &lt;topicmeta>
      &lt;linktitle>Indexing for company specialists&lt;/linktitle>
      &lt;shortdesc>Guidelines for indexing company materials&lt;/shortdesc>
    &lt;/topicmeta>
    &lt;!-- Additional topic references -->
  &lt;/topicref>
&lt;/map></codeblock>
      <p>When link previews for <filepath>indexing.dita</filepath> are
        generated, the link title and short description provided within the
          <xmlelement>topicmeta</xmlelement> element are used.</p>
    </example>
